Text: "I was on the end of my career back in Argentina, felt in love one mont after\
  \ fortunately or unfortunately, I will never know it, 3 friends invited me to make\
  \ a working holiday on New Zealand for a year and I wasn\u2019t sure but on the\
  \ moment I thought, here is a chance to make something different, and hey traveling\
  \ with 3 childhoods friends for one year around two islands in the middle of know\
  \ where believe me, sounds pretty awesome for a young man. \nOctober 2015 everything\
  \ on my life were perfect, I was into a world painted full pink, loving her, finishing\
  \ university project, my friends and family supporting my hold happiness, I remember\
  \ those days and still feeling like a dream. Things were a couple of steps to change,\
  \ if you are on the Top be carful cause if you are not conscious hundred percent\
  \ how did you arrived over there, probably you will be on bottom, faster than you\
  \ think."
